			"rating": 5,
			"text": {
				"text": "After three and a half months of unsuccessful treatment for sinusitis and maxillary sinusitis, the doctors at the Buntić clinic pinpointed the problem and solved it in just 20 minutes. By the next morning, I already felt healthy again and could enjoy life!\nBravo - top marks and my sincere gratitude! I confidently recommend them to everyone!\n\nP.S: and special thanks to Dr. Esad",
				"languageCode": "en"
			},
			"originalText": {
				"text": "After three and a half months of unsuccessful treatment for sinusitis and maxillary sinusitis, the doctors at the Buntić clinic pinpointed the problem and solved it in just 20 minutes. By the next morning, I already felt healthy again and could enjoy life!\nBravo - top marks and my sincere gratitude! I confidently recommend them to everyone!\n\nP.S: and special thanks to Dr. Esad",
				"languageCode": "en"
			},
